      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no scratches, chips, or dents. Inside, the cabin smells new, with the leather and upholstery showing zero signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car performs perfectly, offering a smooth and tight driving experience that mirrors its original factory specifications. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved example that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
