      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits a showroom-grade exterior and an interior that remains in a pristine, original state. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been meticulously scrutinized to ensure it meets the expectations of the most discerning collector. This is an uncompromising investment for those who demand excellence in every facet of their acquisition.",
