    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single week. It looks and smells brand new\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! I\u2019m truly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love the second they get behind the wheel. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
