      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the S54B32 high-pressure die-cast iron block engine. This unit exhibits exceptional mechanical health with a documented VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement utilizing structural foam and plates. The individual throttle bodies are perfectly synchronized, providing crisp throttle response across the entire power band. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a factory variable M differential lock. The suspension retains its original kinematic integrity, and the rod bearings have been serviced preventatively. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the serious enthusiast seeking a purist driving experience.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
