      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that defines 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior with a deep, mirror-like luster and absolutely zero road rash, dings, or swirling. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium upholstery is supple and free of creases, the dashboard is flawless, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, document-backed service history and an engine bay so clean it looks untouched. With exceptionally low mileage and a smooth, tight driving dynamic, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire an immaculate, investment-quality vehicle.",
