    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving atmospheric performance, featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with documented rod bearing replacement and comprehensive subframe reinforcement already completed. Power is channeled through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional torque distribution and corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, and the suspension bushings remain compliant yet firm, preserving the car's legendary telepathic handling. Finished in pristine original paint with no aerodynamic or structural blemishes, this vehicle is a turn-key investment for the purist collector.",
